    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Transforms a map point to a 3D position using a terrain provider.</para>
<para>The 3D point is automatically updated when the map point or terrain provider extent changes, enabling dynamic positioning of 3D elements.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>QML Type: <ref refid="classMapToView3D" kindref="compound">MapToView3D</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
